episodes.title: It's Shane in the Membrane

episodes.title: Jumping the Shark-Pool

episodes.title: Sharks After Dark

episodes.title: Only The Strong Will Enduro

details.title: Season 1
details.description: Street Outlaws explores a world of illegal street racing in Oklahoma City.Created with Sketch.

episodes.title: Go Back To Tulsa!
episodes.description: Track racers from Tulsa call out the 405 with hopes of taking down the "fastest street-raced cars in the country". Farmtruck and AZN attempt a garage sale. Both Murder Nova and Chuck upgrade to twin turbo.

episodes.title: Midwest Fireworks
episodes.description: Big Chief strikes a deal with loudmouth racer Freakin' Rican, allowing him to call out #10 Farmtruck in exchange for bootleg fireworks.There's a shakeup in the middle of the list when #8 Derek gets called out by newcomer #9 Andrade,

episodes.title: Papa's Got A Brand New Bug
episodes.description: AZN and Farmtruck build a Volkswagen bug race car to go out fishing with but have a run-in with the local authorities. The top three on the list compete in a racing extravaganza.

episodes.title: Fastest Chick In OKC
episodes.description: Tina Pierce, known by locals to be the fastest female racer in Oklahoma, calls out #10 Farmtruck. Old family rivalries come to a head when #8 Varley and #9 Andrade Jr. face-off while #6 Chuck and #7 Derek race for a $1000 and the #6 spot.

episodes.title: Straight Out To Cali
episodes.description: The OKC crew brings their cars out to California for a showdown of pride and high stakes betting against the biggest names in California.

episodes.title: Sonoma Mr. Nice Guy
episodes.description: After an expensive overhaul of his car, #2 Murder Nova calls out #1 Daddy Dave in an unforgettable rematch showdown. Freakin' Rican finally gets his shot when he calls out #10 Farmtruck, but an AZN joyride jeopardizes the Farmtruck's gatekeeper standing.

episodes.title: The Rise Of The Crow
episodes.description: Big Chief relinquishes his racemaster duties to another driver so he can race THE CROW back up the list. Tina drops off the list, opening the coveted 10-spot for a round robin competition. Varley's son/driver is a no show. Azn gets stopped by the police.

episodes.title: Drag Week
episodes.description: With the help of some racing legends, Big Chief resurrects his first race car, a '72 Pontiac LeMans he calls The Crow. The OKC's top 3 take on some expert race car builders' best to hold their coveted title of "Fastest Street Cars in the Nation.

episodes.title: Lonestar Smackdown
episodes.description: In the season premiere, Farmtruck and AZN must face-off against newbie racers who want to get on the top ten list. Old state rivalries lead to big brawls when Texas racers LMR want to change the rules on the OKC guys.

episodes.title: Showdown Lowdown
episodes.description: #1 Daddy Dave and #2 Murder Nova square off while best friends #3 Doc and #4 Monza battle on the street for the first time. After installing a secret weapon on his Monte Carlo, Doc is painfully reminded that testing on the street is very illegal.

episodes.title: Build to Mega Race Part III

episodes.title: From Mega to Street
episodes.description: Chief and Shawn take a look back at never-before-aired racing footage.

episodes.title: Doom and Gloom
episodes.description: Everyone loses their spots and has to race to find out where they belong.

episodes.title: Build to Mega Race Part IV
episodes.description: Farmtruck and AZN are scrambling to get their cars ready to race.

episodes.title: Start Me Up
episodes.description: Street Outlaws is back, and the guys in the 405 are making big changes.

episodes.title: Can't You Hear Me Knocking
episodes.description: Chief and Shawn map out a plan to get back into the top spots of the list.

details.title: Season 2
details.description: Street Outlaws explores a world of illegal street racing in Oklahoma City.Created with Sketch.

episodes.title: New Orleans Cookin'
episodes.description: Chief wants to do a "nationwide call out", but also wants to determine if Kye Kelley should be one of the Nation's top 5 drivers. So he sets up a showdown in New Orleans between the 405 and Kye and his Mississippi friends.Dave also wants a rematch for #1.

episodes.title: Let them Eat Crow!
episodes.description: As the racing season winds down, everyone makes a final push to move up the top ten list. Big Chief gets a shot, but Daddy Dave pulls out all the stops to keep the crown. Farmtruck and AZN fish out new competition, but get more than they bargained for.

episodes.title: Vocal Local Yokels
episodes.description: The 405 goes head-to-head in a demolition derby while Farmtruck and AZN answer a nasty callout. Then the legitimacy of the 405's entire list gets called into question, and it comes down to a 405 grudge match.

episodes.title: She's A Good Girl
episodes.description: Chief confirms another driver for the nationwide call out. Farmtruck and AZN play around with the Mad Scientist's new toy: a Tri-Powered Trike. On race night, Shawn tries to get the Murder Nova back to the top of the list. The 405 loses one of their own.

episodes.title: The Southeast's Fastest: Part 1
episodes.description: It's the biggest, most O.G. Cash Days ever! 2 days of racing and 16 of the fastest racers in the Southeast square off. The 405's fastest set their sights on bringing the $16,000 prize home and being crowned the fastest street raced car in the southeast.

episodes.title: Permanent Gatekeeper
episodes.description: Kamikaze takes the El Camino off the list, so Chief decides to round up 4 drivers and have a round robin race for the open 10-spot. Meanwhile, Farmtruck becomes the permanent gatekeeper of The List, and the guys at Midwest give Boosted an ultimatum: win

episodes.title: The Southeast's Fastest: Part 2
episodes.description: On the final night of Cash Days, the remaining 405 racers put their reputation on the line as one of them tries to win $16,000 and be crowned the fastest street racer in the Southeast. Meanwhile, Farmtruck and AZN set their sights on a new World Record.

episodes.title: Texas Grudge
episodes.description: Boosted has set up Grudge Races down in Fort Worth, Texas and decides to hold a Grudge Race school to better prepare the 405 Farmtruck and AZN fish along the way, but get more than they bargain for. Race night gets downright wild in the Lone Star State.

episodes.title: Hearse And The Wichita Curse
episodes.description: Big Chief gets a call out from the 316 area code, Wichita, Kansas. Some of the 405's fastest racers must take on guys with names like the Murder 56 and Superman. Farmtruck and AZN get some seat time in the haunted hearse

episodes.title: Gatekeeper Gate
episodes.description: The fastest gatekeeper in Top Ten List history must defend against the loudest, angriest racers who want a shot at the list. Tensions are running so high, that Big Chief has to call a second race night in one week just to keep racers from coming to blows.
